## Build / debug command

- When you need to build/run the project (TypeScript/Vite build, compile checks, etc.), **prefer `npm run debug`** for this repository.
- The user will then need to reload Foundry to show the updated module
- Only use other scripts (`npm run build`, `npm test`, etc.) if the user explicitly asks.

